{"tid":44083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【羅君兒案翻版】【不斷更新】刀賊逼女戶主碌卡 買$26萬金飾撳機$2萬","createTime":"2016-12-18T03:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T04:13:49.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ed774e61c97a4d04248ab2d576516fa0594d646","tid":44083,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:47:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161218&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56061651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161218%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56061651&d=PtFwCEnN4a7PJ%2F0UQYE76GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=468b8dd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161218%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56061651&h=6828eb89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161218&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56061651</a><br />\n繼去年西貢發生bossini（堡獅龍）創辦人羅定邦的孫女羅君兒遭入屋打劫綁架案，西貢再發生「翻版」事件。3名匪徒昨晚潛入一間獨立屋打劫，其間強行脅持戶主夫婦乘車離去，幸警方及時趕至，經搜索後救出戶主夫婦及拘捕一匪。遇劫男女戶主為著名建築師馬儉思夫婦。<br />\n現場為西貢銀線灣銀臺路碧濤花園一間獨立屋。3名操國語男賊，昨晚7時許持刀闖入上址，綑綁外傭及脅持同樣67歲的馬儉思夫婦進行搜掠，賊人掠去財物但疑嫌錢少，於是脅持馬儉思夫婦前往將軍澳的櫃員機提款。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89N52hv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89N52hv.jpg&h=2c306383&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edb74cd2f2d1796709daedffc415aaefbdb22bd3","tid":44083,"uid":15220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"多謝黨輸入專才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4c9dc9c0ae1345d7d96e1087cb5fad86bcadb9","tid":44083,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:00:31.000Z","msg":"一物治一物<br />\n地產霸權有中國專才"},{"pid":"2a023f78f7ed3150e2039bac07fbc366e9504d87","tid":44083,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:02:14.000Z","msg":"原來尋晚d直升機